  "text": "Dichotomised outcomes will be presented as proportions of participants in each group with the event, and risk ratios with 95% confidence intervals. Relative risks will be analysed using generalised linear models (bireg) using a log link function [CITATION_1] . Additionally, absolute risk reductions and number needed to treat will be presented for interpretability.",
